    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n    <strong>School</strong>&nbsp;necromancy&nbsp;[death, evil];\n    <strong>Level</strong>&nbsp;cleric/oracle 4, inquisitor 4, sorcerer/wizard 4, witch 4;\n    \n    \n    \n    \n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Casting Time</strong>&nbsp;1 standard action<br>\n    <strong>Components</strong>&nbsp;V, S<br>\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Range</strong>&nbsp;20 feet<br>\n    <strong>Area</strong>&nbsp;20-ft.-radius emanation, centered on you<br>\n    \n    \n    <strong>Duration</strong>&nbsp;1 round/level (D)<br>\n    <strong>Saving Throw</strong>&nbsp;Will negates;&nbsp;<strong>Spell Resistance</strong>&nbsp;yes<br>\n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  <p>You gain a shimmering gray aura that feeds on the souls of creatures who die within it. The aura sheds light as a candle. If a creature at -1 or fewer hit points is within the aura at the start of its turn, it must save or die, granting you the benefits of <i>death knell</i>.</p>\n</div>\n",
